					Full Description



		PT First Media Tbk is an Indonesia-based Company engaged provision of media contents and services. The Company has two business segments: cable television (TV) network and Internet and broadband wireless access. For cable TV network segment, the Company provides subscription services for cable TV programs under brand, namely HomeCable. The Company offers broadband communication network, broadband Internet services, broadband wireless access, as well as corporate access network under brand, namely FastNet. The Company also provides data communications service, which is Multiprotocol Label Switching (MPLS) that delivers a broad range of service over fiber optic leased line under brand DataComm. The Company's subsidiaries are PT Margayu Vatri Chantiqa, PT Ayunda Prima Mitra, PT Link Net, PT First Media Production, PT First Media News and PT First Media Television.
» Full Overview of KBLV.JK







