PT First Media Tbk Key Developments

PT First Media Tbk Announces Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Nine Months Ended September 30, 2016
Nov 3 16
PT First Media Tbk announced unaudited consolidated earnings results for the nine months ended September 30, 2016. For the period, the company reported sales and revenue of IDR 1,004,379 million compared to IDR 739,443 million a year ago. Operating loss was IDR 1,209,997 million compared to IDR 1,337,406 million a year ago. Loss before income tax was IDR 1,289,039 million compared to IDR 1,359,224 million a year ago. Loss attributable to equity holders of the parent company was IDR 564,060 million or IDR 324 per basic share compared to IDR 476,410 million or IDR 273 per basic share a year ago. Net cash flows used in operating activities were IDR 298,141 million compared to IDR 451,181 million a year ago. Property, plant and equipment acquisition was IDR 188,350 million compared to IDR 531,750 million a year ago.


PT First Media Tbk Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Six Months Ended June 30, 2016
Jul 31 16
PT First Media Tbk reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the six months ended June 30, 2016. For the six months, the company reported revenues of IDR 664,091 million compared to IDR 475,102 million a year ago. Operating loss was IDR 874,620 million compared to IDR 766,060 million a year ago. Loss before income tax was IDR 862,274 million compared to IDR 838,961 million a year ago. Loss for the period was IDR 685,611 million compared to IDR 632,416 million a year ago. Loss attributable to the equity holders of the parent entity was IDR 389,617 million compared to IDR 276,713 million a year ago. Basic loss per share was IDR 224 compared to IDR 159 a year ago. Net cash flows used in operating activities were IDR 168,460 million compared to IDR 767,629 million a year ago. Acquisition of property, plant and equipment was IDR 243,533 million compared to IDR 242,724 million a year ago. Acquisition of intangible assets was IDR 1,156 million.


PT First Media Tbk, Annual General Meeting, Apr 15, 2016
Mar 30 16
PT First Media Tbk, Annual General Meeting, Apr 15, 2016, at 12:00 Indian Standard Time. Location: Ballroom A, Hotel Aryaduta Tugu Tani Jakarta Jl. Prapatan 44-48 Jakarta 10110 Indonesia Agenda: To approve the Company's Annual Report for the fiscal year that is ended on 31 December 2015; to approve appointment of a Public Accountant Firm to audit the Company's books for 2016 fiscal year and to authorize the Company's Board of Directors to determine the fee for the said Public Accountant along with other requirements for its appointment; and to approve the determination of the Company's Board of Commissioners and Board of Directors and stiuplation of honorarium, benefit, salary, bonus and or other remunerations for the members of the Company's Board of Directors and Board of Commissioners.


