Company Description                    




                        PT. First Media Tbk. (KBLV) operates in the provision of broadband communication network, as well as distributing various electronic signals through the network. KBLV's products and services include FastNet, HomeCable and DataComm. KBLV's main revenue is derived primarily from the distribution of television programs in Jakarta, Bogor, Tangerang, Bekasi, Surabaya, Bali and Pekanbaru. KBLV was listed on Indonesia Stock Exchange in 2000 under the Development Board. The company was founded in 1994 and based in Jakarta, Indonesia.                    


